data.description: This 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home is a substantial opportunity, boasting a total of 2,748 square feet. An attractive prospect for both investors and first-time homeowners, this property offers plenty. Arriving, you're greeted by a spacious driveway leading to the 1-car garage. The three bedrooms are generously sized, accommodating family or guests with ease. Step outside to the vast screened-in patio, perfect for entertainment and offers room for future expansion. The property holds endless possibilities for crafting your ideal outdoor space. Given its appealing features and potential, this property is expected to move quickly. Seize this promising opportunity while it's available
